{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"猛听得身手有人轻","listener":null,"text":"施主留步，请听小僧一言。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":2,"line_end":4},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"向房内指了指","listener":null,"text":"请施主回房说话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":10,"line_end":12},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"敢问大师有何事见告？","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":20,"line_end":22},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"开口说","listener":null,"text":"小僧早就看出施主是一位深藏不露的高人，敝寺今天发生的事情，施主也早已看在眼里。  敢问施主适才逾窗而出，可是想去后殿中一看究竟？","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":24,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_wang_yi_ping","speaker_name":"王一萍","listener":null,"text":"不错，除非大师将其中真情见告，使在下确知不人去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":28,"line_end":30},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"爽快地","listener":null,"text":"说来已是三十年前的事情，那时小僧年仅九岁。  记得那天山中正值狂风暴雨，从庙外跌跌撞撞走进一个人来。  这人身上受了极重内伤，双臂折断，两腿伤得极重，有几刀已伤及腿骨。  这人纵使治好，也将落个终生残废。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":32,"line_end":40},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"毒儒","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"无碍将这段往事讲完，接着又道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":76,"line_end":78},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"王一萍问道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":82,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_wang_yi_ping","speaker_name":"王一萍","listener":null,"text":"无碍和尚道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":84,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_wu_ai_he_shang","speaker_name":"无碍和尚","listener":null,"text":"王一萍知道再问也是无用，遂改问道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":86,"line_end":88},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"改问","listener":null,"text":"无碍和尚道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":90,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_wu_ai_he_shang","speaker_name":"无碍和尚","listener":null,"text":"王一萍想了想，道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":92,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_wu_ai_he_shang","speaker_name":"无碍和尚","listener":null,"text":"无碍和尚道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":96,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_wu_ai_he_shang","speaker_name":"无碍和尚","listener":null,"text":"王一萍想要知道的不仅是干瘦老人与憨山寺结怨经过，还有今夜将发生的事情。  无碍和尚的一番追叙，仅满足了一半，但无碍和尚不愿多说，而且显有阻止王一萍前去之意。  无碍和尚如此，反使王一萍更觉得非去见识一次不可。  无碍和尚两目如距，王一萍心意才动，无碍和尚早已看出，眉心微微皱了一下，左手中食两指疾探王一萍睡穴，沉声道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":98,"line_end":106}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_wang_yi_ping","name":"王一萍","alias":[],"identity":"湘江一龙龙灵飞之徒","faction":"","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":6,"one_line":"湘江一龙龙灵飞的弟子，身怀龙形九式绝学","personality":{"traits":["侠义","好奇","自信","冲动","机敏","正义感强"],"speech_style":"直率坦荡","temperament":"热血冲动"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_wu_ai","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"由敌转友"}],"known_skills":["skill_long_xing_jiu_shi"],"related_skills":["skill_long_xing_jiu_shi"],"rag_refs":[8],"source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"王一萍托开后窗"}]},{"id":"char_wu_ai_he_shang","name":"无碍和尚","alias":["无碍"],"identity":"憨山寺僧人","faction":"faction_han_shan_si","role":"npc","archetype":"monk","rank":4,"one_line":"憨山寺僧人，被小女孩使诈伤了一剑","personality":{"traits":["固执","忠诚","好胜","直率","刚烈"],"speech_style":"出家人语气","temperament":"刚烈急躁"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_miao_chen","type":"师徒","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"尊师"},{"target":"char_wang_yi_ping","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"由敌转友"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[8],"source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":8,"line_end":8,"text":"原来就是白天被小女孩使诈伤了一剑的无碍和尚"}]},{"id":"char_miao_chen","name":"妙尘","alias":["衰病老僧"],"identity":"憨山寺掌门","faction":"faction_han_shan_si","role":"npc","archetype":"monk","rank":5,"one_line":"憨山寺掌门，身患重病但仍具威严","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","慈悲","坚毅","守信","睿智","威严"],"speech_style":"老僧口吻","temperament":"沉稳庄严"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_wu_ai","type":"师徒","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"师徒"},{"target":"char_gan_shou_lao_ren","type":"宿敌","intensity":